102.8	War_and_Peace	War and Peace	War and Peace (Russian: , Pre-reform Russian: «Война и миръ») is a novel by the Russian author Leo Tolstoy, first published in 1869. The work is epic in scale and is regarded as one of the most important works of world literature. It is considered Tolstoy's finest literary achievement, along with his other major prose work Anna Karenina (1873–1877).	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/05/WarAndPeace.jpg/150px-WarAndPeace.jpg
